<topic id="display-problems-linux">
  <title>Display Problems on Linux/Solaris</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Performance Problems<indexterm>problems on Linux/Solaris</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>Display problems like screen freeze or momentary menu pop-ups during mouse movements over
      screen on Linux or Solaris can be solved by <xref href="set-parameter-in-startup-script.dita"
        >adding the startup parameter</xref>
      <parmname>-Dsun.java2d.pmoffscreen=false</parmname>.</p>
  </body>
</topic>
